NodeVisitor<SoyNode,com.google.common.collect.ImmutableMap<String,String>>
public class GenerateParseInfoVisitor
extends AbstractSoyNodeVisitor<com.google.common.collect.ImmutableMap<String,String>>

Visitor for generating Java classes containing the parse info.

Important: Do not use outside of Soy code (treat as superpackage-private).

AbstractNodeVisitor.exec(N) should be called on a full parse tree.

For an example Soy file and its corresponding generated code, see 

     [tests_dir]/com/google/template/soy/test_data/AaaBbbCcc.soy
     [tests_dir]/com/google/template/soy/test_data/AaaBbbCccSoyInfo.java
